h1 lit

!= messages()

- if (count)
  p Display all #{count} text(s)
  ul#texts
    - each text in texts
      a.view(href=base + '/text/' + text.id)
        li= text.title
  p
    | Click
    a(href=base + '/text/add') here 
    | to add another text.
- else
  p 
    | It looks like you have no texts!
  p
    | Click
    a(href=base + '/text/add') here 
    | to create a text.